**/*.log
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*

# OS files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# TypeScript
**/tsconfig.tsbuildinfo

# Editor
.vscode/
.idea/

# Misc
**/.turbo/
